gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Heat 121, Kings 110
gameRecap.excerpt: Bam Adebayo (28 points, 10 rebounds, seven assists) and Jaime Jaquez Jr. (26 points (20 in second half), five rebounds, 12-17 FG) combine for 54 to lead the Heat over the Kings, 121-110.  Keegan Murray (28 points, six 3PM) and DeAaron Fox (27 points, eight rebounds, six assists) combined for 55 points for the Kings in the losing effort.  The Heat improve to 32-25 on the season, while the Kings fall to 33-24.
